9 . 4 | . 6 . | . . 5 
---------------------
. 7 . | 3 . . | . 1 2 
1 2 . | . . 7 | 4 . . 
. 4 9 | 2 . 6 | . . 7 

‚úÖ Solved Sudoku Puzzle:

7 8 5 | 4 3 9 | 1 2 6 
6 1 2 | 8 7 5 | 3 4 9 
4 9 3 | 6 2 1 | 5 7 8 
---------------------
8 5 7 | 9 4 3 | 2 6 1 
2 6 1 | 7 5 8 | 9 3 4 
9 3 4 | 1 6 2 | 7 8 5 
---------------------
5 7 8 | 3 9 4 | 6 1 2 
1 2 6 | 5 8 7 | 4 9 3 
3 4 9 | 2 1 6 | 8 5 7

